OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778144787
OL,3,CNurse diagnosed with rare ovarian
OL,4,Ccancer urges people to 'get checked
OL,5,Cout'
OL,7,FA Kent nurse who was diagnosed with a
OL,8,Frare cancer is urging people to "get
OL,9,Fchecked out" ahead of World Ovarian
OL,10,FCancer Day.
OL,12,FCharlotte Flannery, who works as a
OL,13,Fsurgical services matron at Medway
OL,14,FMaritime Hospital, told ITV Meridian
OL,15,Fshe's sharing her own story to raise
OL,16,Fawareness of the disease.
OL,18,FThe mother of six noticed something
OL,19,Fwas wrong with herself, when she began
OL,20,Fto experience ovulation pain that
OL,21,F"just did not go away".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
