PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778144787
OL,3,CNurse diagnosed with rare ovarian
OL,4,Ccancer urges people to 'get checked
OL,5,Cout'
OL,7,FShe said: "It (pain) was tracking down
OL,8,Fmy leg. Very uncomfortable. Not the
OL,9,Fclassic comes and gos pain.
OL,11,F"It was just quite intense and pain
OL,12,Frelief didn't help, so that was the
OL,13,Ffirst sign for me that something was
OL,14,Fwrong."
OL,16,FTests later revealed that she had an
OL,17,F8cm mass on her right ovary, which
OL,18,Fdoctors initially thought was a benign
OL,19,Fdermoid cyst.
OL,26,@oD@OpmoD@Tpn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778144787
OL,3,CNurse diagnosed with rare ovarian
OL,4,Ccancer urges people to 'get checked
OL,5,Cout'
OL,7,FMs Flannery underwent surgery to
OL,8,Fremove the cyst, but, when analysed,
OL,9,Fit revealed a devastating diagnosis.
OL,11,FThe cyst, in fact, contained a brain
OL,12,Ftumor and spinal cord cancer - of
OL,13,Fwhich there have been fewer than 100
OL,14,Frecorded cases.
OL,16,FShe added: "I woke up in recovery and
OL,17,FI said 'oh it's a dermoid cyst. These
OL,18,Fare non-cancerous.'
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778144787
OL,3,CNurse diagnosed with rare ovarian
OL,4,Ccancer urges people to 'get checked
OL,5,Cout'
OL,7,F"Dermoid's can contain any part that
OL,8,Fmakes up the human body, so hair,
OL,9,Fbones, teeth.
OL,11,F"Unfortunately, mine had
OL,12,FMedulloblastoma and it also had
OL,13,Fprimitive neuroectodermal tumours -
OL,14,Fboth of which are childhood cancers
OL,15,Fand incredibly rare.
OL,17,F"So these childhood cancers were
OL,18,Fgrowing in the dermoid on my ovary."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778144787
OL,3,CNurse diagnosed with rare ovarian
OL,4,Ccancer urges people to 'get checked
OL,5,Cout'
OL,7,FFurther tests found that the cancer
OL,8,Fhad spread and that Ms Flannery needed
OL,9,Fsurgery to remove three tumors.
OL,11,FShe has recently finished treatment,
OL,12,Fbut, due to the rarity of her cancer,
OL,13,Fher longterm prognosis remains
OL,14,Funcertain.
OL,16,FMs Flannery said running has helped
OL,17,Fher to cope through treatment,
OL,18,Fcompeting in two London Marathons,
OL,19,Fsince receiving her initial diagnosis.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778144787
OL,3,CNurse diagnosed with rare ovarian
OL,4,Ccancer urges people to 'get checked
OL,5,Cout'
OL,7,F"It's my processing time. It's my me
OL,8,Ftime and also it put me in the best
OL,9,Fmental and physical space to take on
OL,10,Fthat treatment.
OL,12,F"The professor has said he's never
OL,13,Fseen anyone recover so well from the
OL,14,Ftreatment I had and I think a lot of
OL,15,Fthat is because I went into treatment
OL,16,Fliterally marathon-fit."
OL,18,FMs Flannery has since returned to work
OL,19,Fand is encouraging anyone with their
OL,20,Fown concerns to find help.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
