PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778144787
OL,3,CNurse diagnosed with rare ovarian
OL,4,Ccancer urges people to 'get checked
OL,5,Cout'
OL,7,FShe said: "If it's not right. Any of
OL,8,Fthe symptoms, bloating, struggling to
OL,9,Fpass urine, night sweats, irregular
OL,10,Fperiods, anything that's not right for
OL,11,Fyou, you need to go and get it seen
OL,12,Fto."
